-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
TERRAFORM FILES TO IGNORE (CRITICAL)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Terraform state files (contain state and secrets)
*.tfstate
.tfstate.

Local provider/module cache directory (downloaded content)
.terraform/

Crash log files
crash.log
crash.*.log

Terraform CLI configuration files
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

Local backup/plan files (often contain sensitive plan data)
*.tfplan
*.backup

Ignore the random suffix file
.terraform.lock.hcl

